jor political transitions occurred through conferences papers and publications we bring scholars from around the world to analyze how japan is transforming contact kenji kushida publications cover entrepreneurship in japan's ict sector opportunities and protection from japan's telecommunications regulatory regime shift kenji kushida social science japan journal 2011 html+ cover spending without taxation filp and the politics of public finance in japan gene park stanford university press 2011 buy+ cover corporations in evolving diversity cognition governance and institutions masahiko aoki oxford university press 2010 buy+ search aparc search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages research news shorenstein aparc announces three new political economy titles april 15 2011 news support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 723 9741 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
